---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="About me" id="about">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    <p class="text-center text-sm md:px-16 md:text-lg">
      Hello! I'm Adithya Krishna Eemani, a dynamic professional deeply rooted in
      Computer Science and Engineering, specializing in cutting-edge domains
      such as <span class="text-primary"
        >Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning</span
      >. My unwavering commitment centers around catalyzing transformative
      change through innovative solutions, operational efficiency, and
      pioneering code development. I am dedicated to empowering businesses and
      enhancing lives by creating groundbreaking technological solutions. If you
      seek a motivated and <span class="text-primary">skilled developer</span> with
      a fervent passion for innovation, then I would love to hear from you!
    </p>
  </Fragment>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row">
    <a
      href="/adithya-krishna.pdf"
      target="_blank"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="book" class="h-8" />
      <span>My Resume</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adithyakrishnaeemani"
      target="_blank"
      class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-current px-6 py-4 lg:w-48"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="linkedin" class="h-8 md:h-8 mr-2" />
      <span class="text-base">Connect</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
